* Entrance Screen, Cullen House, Cullen, Moray (1767)
* Bridge, Osterley Park ()
* Entrance screen, Syon House (1769)
* Fishing, Boat &amp; Bath House, Kedleston Hall (1770–71)
* Circular Temple, Audley End House, Essex (1771)
* Lion Bridge, Alnwick (1773)
* Stag Lodge, Saltram House, Devon ()
* The Stables, Featherstone entrance &amp; Huntwick arch Nostell Priory (1776)
