* Three paintings by Welsh artist Christopher Williams: &quot;Ceridwen&quot; (1910) and &quot;Branwen&quot; (1915) at the Glynn Vivian Art Gallery, and &quot;Blodeuwedd&quot; (1930) at the Newport Museum
* &quot;Mabinogion&quot; sheep problem

